{"tid":1324274,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"RTX 2080 HEVC解碼問題","createTime":"2019-07-16T13:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:31:39.000Z","uid":162651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a50c5eedaf33062506845c54a762ef3485c130a6","tid":1324274,"uid":162651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:40:47.000Z","msg":"小弟之前因為工作需要用NOTE 9手機拍左幾條4K60FPS嘅片 影片編碼較左去HEVC <br />\n顯示卡用緊 RTX2080 諗住睇到HEVC編碼嘅片 點知一開條片 頭2秒好順之後就開始疾<br />\nCPU升到100% 係工作管理員度睇 張卡見唔到佢有解碼 請問有咩方法可以解決到?<br />\n睇其他片無事 仲有5K片都睇唔到 但YOUTUBE 8K又好順暢 真係唔知做乜春<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: PLAYER用緊POTPLAYER 加埋【強國】完美解碼個PACK 咪屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為唔知仲有咩解碼PACK先用強國貨...  <br />\n<br />\n5K片編碼資訊:<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/16/GRHWpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2FGRHWpa.png&h=9d7f24c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNOTE9 4K60FPS 編碼資訊:<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/16/olzgaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2FolzgaY.png&h=7c7c375b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54c2e244ecfa8230eda3d27fe7c44103b04fd53f","tid":1324274,"uid":79829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"我都係用2080<br />\nsend條片黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f51553ad5dcaa9571d299682788fb30a9526785","tid":1324274,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"Microsoft store唔係有hevc extension download?"},{"pid":"00fcedbe2168253de257897fce6a26c974aff3cc","tid":1324274,"uid":7992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"potplayer要set<br />\n你可以試下google搵 potplayer硬解4k<br />\n會有教學 set完之後應該run得順"},{"pid":"454e4152b46911b5a3e11878849661ae5bd60aee","tid":1324274,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00fcedbe2168253de257897fce6a26c974aff3cc","tid":1324274,"uid":7992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"potplayer要set<br />\n你可以試下google搵 potplayer硬解4k<br />\n會有教學 set完之後應該run得順"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"我無set過野都可以硬解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d312eddde8eca269fd050ad4593098b18276f7","tid":1324274,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"potplayer唔係preset硬解咩？點解仲要裝pack？"},{"pid":"99063d8269433d43c2ef2860c79204c01b4591d3","tid":1324274,"uid":162651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"裝PACK原因係因為解碼唔順先裝 點知裝完都係一樣<br />\n<br />\nH/W 係硬解 S/W係軟解 <br />\n條5K片可以較S/W或者無S/W 有無開分別都唔大 CPU 100%<br />\nFPS可以勉強保持到60 有時都係卡<br />\n但係HEVC就無得俾我較<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1yOyw4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1yOyw4.png&h=4d30956e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總知唔知做咩睇唔到呢啲片 剪片都唔順暢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}